{
  "page": "Caltrops",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(248, 233, 208);border:none;\">Caltrops</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Caltrops_(The_Rise_of_the_Dragon).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"The Caltrops (The Rise of the Dragon).jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3b/The_Caltrops_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/350px-The_Caltrops_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"465\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3b/The_Caltrops_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/525px-The_Caltrops_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3b/The_Caltrops_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/700px-The_Caltrops_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>The Caltrops by John McCambridge for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tumbleton\" title=\"Tumbleton\">Tumbleton</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Participants</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>Ser/Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Marq_Ambrose\" title=\"Marq Ambrose\">Marq Ambrose</a></li><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Owen_Fossoway\" title=\"Owen Fossoway\">Owen Fossoway</a></li><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/George_Graceford\" title=\"George Graceford\">George Graceford</a></li><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Hobert_Hightower\" title=\"Hobert Hightower\">Hobert Hightower</a></li><li>Ser/Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Leygood_(father_of_Lucas)\" title=\"Leygood (father of Lucas)\">Leygood</a></li><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Tyler_Norcross\" title=\"Tyler Norcross\">Tyler Norcross</a></li><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Unwin_Peake\" title=\"Unwin Peake\">Unwin Peake</a></li><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Victor_Risley\" title=\"Victor Risley\">Victor Risley</a></li><li>Ser/Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Richard_Rodden\" title=\"Richard Rodden\">Richard Rodden</a></li><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Roxton\" title=\"Jon Roxton\">Jon Roxton</a></li><li>Three unnamed lords and landed knights</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Goal</th><td>\nKill <a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Hammer\" title=\"Hugh Hammer\">Hugh Hammer</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Ulf_White\" title=\"Ulf White\">Ulf White</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>Hugh is killed by Jon Roxton</li><li>Ulf is poisoned by Hobert Hightower</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Casualties</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>Ser Jon Roxton</li><li>Ser Hobert Hightower</li><li>Casualties of the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Battle_of_Tumbleton\" title=\"Second Battle of Tumbleton\">Second Battle of Tumbleton</a></li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Caltrops</b> were thirteen nobles from <a href=\"/index.php/The_Reach\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Reach\">the Reach</a> who plotted to kill the <a href=\"/index.php/Two_Betrayers\" title=\"Two Betrayers\">Two Betrayers</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>. They were called the Caltrops after the inn in <a href=\"/index.php/Tumbleton\" title=\"Tumbleton\">Tumbleton</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Bloody_Caltrops\" title=\"Bloody Caltrops\">Bloody Caltrops</a>, where they met to conspire.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Members\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Members</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Caltrops&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Battle_of_Tumbleton\" title=\"First Battle of Tumbleton\">First Battle of Tumbleton</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ulf_White\" title=\"Ulf White\">Ulf White</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Hammer\" title=\"Hugh Hammer\">Hugh Hammer</a> defected from the <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">blacks</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">greens</a> and had their <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Silverwing\" title=\"Silverwing\">Silverwing</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Vermithor\" title=\"Vermithor\">Vermithor</a>, burn the town of <a href=\"/index.php/Tumbleton\" title=\"Tumbleton\">Tumbleton</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> While the greens' commanders regrouped in Tumbleton and planned how to attack the black-held <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>, the two baseborn <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonriders\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragonriders\">dragonriders</a> proved difficult to deal with. Ulf desired <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a>, while Hugh had designs on claiming the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>. Hugh wore a black iron crown, enraging Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_Targaryen_(son_of_Viserys_I)\" title=\"Daeron Targaryen (son of Viserys I)\">Daeron Targaryen</a>. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Roger_Corne\" title=\"Roger Corne\">Roger Corne</a> knocked the crown off, which led to Hugh nailing three horseshoes to Roger's skull. Corne's supporters tried to intervene, resulting in three dead and twelve wounded.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The enthusiastic Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Unwin_Peake\" title=\"Unwin Peake\">Unwin Peake</a> and the somewhat reluctant Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Hobert_Hightower\" title=\"Hobert Hightower\">Hobert Hightower</a> gathered eleven other lords and landed knights to the cellar of a Tumbleton inn called the <a href=\"/index.php/Bloody_Caltrops\" title=\"Bloody Caltrops\">Bloody Caltrops</a>, where they debated over how and when to kill the Two Betrayers. The drunkard Ulf would be an easier target, as Hugh was protected by lackeys. After much deliberation, they determined to kill the dragonriders and claim their dragons while in Tumbleton. Prince Daeron was brought to the cellar by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Owen_Fossoway\" title=\"Owen Fossoway\">Owen Fossoway</a> and given warrants for the execution of the Two Betrayers by Lord Peake. Daeron eagerly affixed his seal.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The Caltrops planned their coup against Ulf and Hugh to occur two days later. However, the greens' army was awoken on that designated day by an attack by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Addam_Velaryon\" title=\"Addam Velaryon\">Addam Velaryon</a>, beginning the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Battle_of_Tumbleton\" title=\"Second Battle of Tumbleton\">Second Battle of Tumbleton</a>. Ulf drunkenly slept through the battle, but Hugh rushed to the stables so he could ride to Vermithor. However, Hugh was cut down there by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Roxton\" title=\"Jon Roxton\">Jon Roxton</a>. Despite wielding the blade <a href=\"/index.php/Orphan-Maker\" title=\"Orphan-Maker\">Orphan-Maker</a>, Jon was then slain by Hugh's men. Eight of the Caltrops were dead by the end of Second Tumbleton, including Owen Fossoway, <a href=\"/index.php/Marq_Ambrose\" title=\"Marq Ambrose\">Marq Ambrose</a>, and Jon Roxton. <a href=\"/index.php/Richard_Rodden\" title=\"Richard Rodden\">Richard Rodden</a> died from his wounds the following day, leaving only four plotters. However, these included the ringleaders, Unwin Peake and Hobert Hightower.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The next morning after the Second Tumbleton, Hobert Hightower met with Ulf to plan the attack on King's Landing and provided two casks of wine, <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dornish</a> red and poisoned <a href=\"/index.php/Arbor\" title=\"Arbor\">Arbor</a> gold. Hobert expected to sip the red while Ulf drank the gold, but the dragonrider was suspicious of Hobert's behavior and asked for the red to be saved for later. Rather than give up the surviving Caltrops, Hobert decided to drink the poisoned gold with Ulf, which killed both of them. Following Ulf's death, Lord Peake failed to find a dragonrider for Silverwing and decided to lead the diminishing green army away from Tumbleton and back to the heart of the Reach.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Members\">Members</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Caltrops&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Members\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><b>Slain during the Second Battle of Tumbleton:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Ambrose\" title=\"House Ambrose\"><img alt=\"House Ambrose.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/69/House_Ambrose.svg/20px-House_Ambrose.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/69/House_Ambrose.svg/30px-House_Ambrose.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/69/House_Ambrose.svg/40px-House_Ambrose.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser/Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Marq_Ambrose\" title=\"Marq Ambrose\">Marq Ambrose</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\"><img alt=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/20px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/30px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/40px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Owen_Fossoway\" title=\"Owen Fossoway\">Owen Fossoway</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Leygood\" title=\"House Leygood\"><img alt=\"House Leygood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/69/House_Leygood.svg/20px-House_Leygood.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/69/House_Leygood.svg/30px-House_Leygood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/69/House_Leygood.svg/40px-House_Leygood.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser/Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Leygood_(father_of_Lucas)\" title=\"Leygood (father of Lucas)\">Leygood</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Norcross\" title=\"House Norcross\"><img alt=\"House Norcross.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a7/House_Norcross.svg/20px-House_Norcross.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a7/House_Norcross.svg/30px-House_Norcross.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a7/House_Norcross.svg/40px-House_Norcross.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Tyler_Norcross\" title=\"Tyler Norcross\">Tyler Norcross</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Roxton\" title=\"House Roxton\"><img alt=\"House Roxton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cb/House_Roxton.svg/20px-House_Roxton.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cb/House_Roxton.svg/30px-House_Roxton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cb/House_Roxton.svg/40px-House_Roxton.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Roxton\" title=\"Jon Roxton\">Jon Roxton</a>, killed by <a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Hammer\" title=\"Hugh Hammer\">Hugh Hammer</a>'s men after killing Hugh<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Three other <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lords</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Landed_knight\" title=\"Landed knight\">landed knights</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<p><b>Died in the aftermath of the Second Battle of Tumbleton:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\"><img alt=\"House Hightower.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/20px-House_Hightower.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/30px-House_Hightower.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/40px-House_Hightower.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Hobert_Hightower\" title=\"Hobert Hightower\">Hobert Hightower</a>, died alongside <a href=\"/index.php/Ulf_White\" title=\"Ulf White\">Ulf White</a> when he shared the <a href=\"/index.php/Poison\" title=\"Poison\">poisoned</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a> meant for Ulf<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Rodden\" title=\"House Rodden\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/20px-None.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/30px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/40px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser/Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Richard_Rodden\" title=\"Richard Rodden\">Richard Rodden</a>, took an arrow during the battle and died the following day<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<p><b>Survived the Dance of the Dragons:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Graceford\" title=\"House Graceford\"><img alt=\"House Graceford.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/74/House_Graceford.svg/20px-House_Graceford.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/74/House_Graceford.svg/30px-House_Graceford.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/74/House_Graceford.svg/40px-House_Graceford.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/George_Graceford\" title=\"George Graceford\">George Graceford</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Peake\" title=\"House Peake\"><img alt=\"House Peake.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b2/House_Peake.svg/20px-House_Peake.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b2/House_Peake.svg/30px-House_Peake.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b2/House_Peake.svg/40px-House_Peake.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Unwin_Peake\" title=\"Unwin Peake\">Unwin Peake</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Risley\" title=\"House Risley\"><img alt=\"House Risley.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Risley.svg/20px-House_Risley.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Risley.svg/30px-House_Risley.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5b/House_Risley.svg/40px-House_Risley.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Victor_Risley\" title=\"Victor Risley\">Victor Risley</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Caltrops&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Men may plot and plan and scheme, but they had best pray as well, for no plan made by men has ever withstood the whims of <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">the gods</a> above.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;writings of <a href=\"/index.php/Gyldayn\" title=\"Gyldayn\">Gyldayn</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Caltrops&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.00</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.01</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.02</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.03</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_drag